any books they&#39;ve
 written, or how many &quot;universities&quot; they&#39;ve given. When =
something knows how you think, what you are perceiving, and how it&#39;s being =
perceived, you can&#39;t prevent yourself from being deceived, or more like pla=
yed with. I know I&#39;ll be deceived, and tricked, and I tell them have fun wi=
th that, cuz I don&#39;t really care. I&#39;m not after any particular spirit, or p=
iece of knowledge.  

 When these voices tell someone not to share the inf=
ormation, that&#39;s even thinner ice to on!

 I still, everyday, question the=
 value of this work, and if it warrents continuing. I can do this on my own=
, but I don&#39;t want to drag the unitiated into hell with me! I find the comm=
unication mode itself facsinating, and don&#39;t expect that profound paranorma=
l knowledge others seem to seek. I don&#39;t care who is talking through the bo=
x.  I think those seeking those bits of profound knowledge, or secrets will=
 get lead right down the rabbit hole.


